<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy | Orinzent</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Outfit:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #334155;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .section-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #e2e8f0 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
            margin: 3rem 0;
        }
        .accent-dot {
            height: 6px;
            width: 6px;
            background-color: #6366f1;
            border-radius: 99px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        .nav-blur {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="selection:bg-indigo-50 selection:text-indigo-700">

    <!-- Minimal Header -->
    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 nav-blur">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-7 h-7 bg-indigo-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">O</span>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-lg tracking-tight text-slate-900 uppercase">Orinzent</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Calculator</span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="pt-40 pb-32 px-6">
        <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            
            <!-- Hero Header -->
            <header class="mb-20">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium flex items-center">
                    <span class="inline-block w-4 h-[2px] bg-indigo-500 mr-3"></span>
                    Last updated: January 2026
                </p>
            </header>

            <!-- Overview -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center">
                    Overview
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    This Calculator app is built with a fundamental commitment to user privacy. We do not require account creation, and most core features are designed to work entirely offline. Our philosophy is simple: we do not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or contacts.
                </p>
            </section>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Data Collection -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Collection</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        We do not collect or store personal data. All calculations and inputs remain strictly on your device.
                    </p>
                    <p class="pl-5 border-l-2 border-indigo-100">
                        <span class="text-slate-900 font-semibold">AI Calculator:</span> If you use the AI Calculator feature, the text you enter may be processed temporarily to generate responses. This data is transient, processed in real-time, and is never stored or linked to your identity.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Data Storage -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Storage</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Some data may be stored locally on your device for functionality. This data is never transmitted to any external server:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                    <li class="flex items-center text-slate-600">
                        <span class="accent-dot"></span> Calculation history
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center text-slate-600">
                        <span class="accent-dot"></span> App preferences (theme, number format, settings)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Data Retention & Deletion -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                        All local data remains on your device until you manually clear it or uninstall the app. We do not retain any user data on external servers.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Deletion</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                        You can delete your data by clearing app data in your device settings or uninstalling the app. This permanently removes all stored data.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Third-Party Services -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    This app does not use third-party analytics, ads, or tracking services. If AI functionality is utilized, it may rely on local or external processing models, but no personally identifiable information is collected or stored.
                </p>
            </section>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Permissions & Children -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Permissions</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                        The app does not request sensitive permissions such as location, contacts, or camera access.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Children’s Privacy</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                        This app does not knowingly collect personal data from children and is safe for general audiences.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Changes -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be reflected directly on this page.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Final Contact -->
            <section class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t-4 border-indigo-600">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Contact</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8">If you have any questions, please contact us at:</p>
                <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com" class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 transition-colors break-all">
                    your-orinzent@gmail.com
                </a>
            </section>

        </article>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
